Responsibilities

  Part of the team, to define and deliver modern infrastructure architectures for public and hybrid cloud solutions based on the Microsoft Azure cloud and the broader Microsoft technology stack
  Provide technical and consulting knowledge to clients on proper governance to ensure stability
  Support infrastructure project deployment efforts as directed on projects
  Support systems integration testing (SIT), component integration testing (CIT), and user acceptance testing (UAT)


Requirements

  Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Information Technology or equivalent
  Microsoft Certified: Azure Administrator Associate
  Microsoft Certified: Azure Solutions Architect Expert
  experience in systems engineering or infrastructure

